HEADWORD: Pinweed
<hw>Pin"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genus <gen>Lechea</gen>, low North American herbs
with branching stems, and very small and abundant leaves and
flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

